                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/6323.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-23T16:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 23, 1913—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>29. I have given a copy of the Government’s version of the killing of the
                    President and Vice President to the Associated Press and will <pb facs="0836"
                        n="732" xml:id="pg_732"/> ask the Department to accept it as emanating from
                    this Embassy. This is requested in view of the pressure upon the Embassy at the
                    moment.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
